Liverpool Defeats 10-Man Everton 2-0 in English Premier League

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-10-01T13:51:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-01/liverpool-defeats-10-man-everton-2-0-in-english-premier-league.html
Liverpool scored twice in the second
half to defeat 10-man Everton 2-0 in English soccer’s Premier
League.  Andy Carroll scored in the 71st minute and  Luis Suarez 
added the second goal 11 minutes later as Liverpool won for the
fourth time in its last five league visits to Goodison Park.  Everton’s Jack Rodwell received a red card for a challenge
on Suarez in the 23rd minute. Toffees goalkeeper  Tim Howard  also
stopped  Dirk Kuyt ’s penalty kick just before halftime.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  